  "prompt": "How do I watch Formula 1 online in India?",
  "response": "To watch Formula 1 online in India, you have a few options:\n\n1. **F1 TV Pro**: This is the official streaming service of Formula 1, offering live streaming of all races, practice sessions, and qualifying. It also includes additional features like telemetry data and onboard cameras. You can subscribe directly through the F1 TV website.\n\n2. **Disney+ Hotstar**: Formula 1 races are typically broadcast live on Disney+ Hotstar in India. You\u2019ll need a subscription to access the live streams and additional content.\n\n3. **Sky Sports F1**: If you have a subscription to Sky Sports, you can watch Formula 1 through their online streaming platform. However, this option may require a VPN if you're not located in a region that allows access.\n\n4. **VPN Services**: If you\u2019re interested in accessing broadcasts from other regions (like Sky Sports or ESPN), you can use a VPN to connect to a different server.\n\n5. **YouTube**: While you won't be able to watch live races, the official Formula 1 YouTube channel provides highlights, interviews, and other related content.\n\nMake sure to check the availability of these services as they can vary by season or be subject to specific licensing agreements.",
